### Get all authors
GET http://localhost:3000/authors

### Create author
POST http://localhost:3000/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName":"Jane",
  "lastName":"Doe",
  "bio":"Example author",
  "birthdate":"1975-10-01",
  "nationality":"American"
}

### Get all books
GET http://localhost:3000/books

### Create book (replace authorId with a real one from authors result)
POST http://localhost:3000/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title":"My Example Book",
  "authorId":"<replace-with-author-id>",
  "isbn":"978-0-123456-47-2",
  "publisher":"ACME Press",
  "publishedDate":"2020-01-01",
  "pages":320,
  "genre":"Fiction",
  "summary":"Short description"
}

### Update book (partial)
PUT http://localhost:3000/books/<bookId>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "genre":"Sci-Fi"
}

### Delete book
DELETE http://localhost:3000/books/<bookId>
